demo.ilbm - a picture to make people
            quickly realise what this program
            does, and if they want it.
ats.guide - this very text you're reading.
            Containing the documentation for
            the program.
ats.c     - the C source.
DMakefile - a makefile for it.
Readme    - a short description.
@endnode contents

